plugin_name: AI Smart Programming Assistant
plugin_description: An AI-powered smart programming assistant plugin for MT Manager, providing intelligent code analysis, optimization suggestions, and issue diagnosis services. Deeply integrated with AI model, supporting full-text analysis and quick code snippet diagnosis. Also includes practical development tools such as encoding/decoding, hash calculation, and timestamp conversion to comprehensively improve mobile programming efficiency.
plugin_author: Kang Ge
plugin_website: Official Website
plugin_source: Open Source
support_author: Support Author
support_author_summary: Sponsor to support plugin development
support_author_title: Support Author
support_message: This open-source plugin and its free AI models are facing increasing server, computing, and maintenance costs that have become difficult for an individual to sustain long-term. To avoid service interruptions and ensure future updates and stable operation, we have opened a voluntary sponsorship channel.\n\nAll sponsorships will be used exclusively for server renewal, computing costs, and project maintenance. Thank you for your long-term support, and we hope to continue providing open-source and free AI services together with you.
